::Feline::

She stood up and walked over to Skulletron.  She stood behind him and 
ran her hands down his chest and back up to his shoulders. She purred 
in his ear and stood upright.  She walked back to her chair, swaying 
her hips as she walked and sat down.
She the turned to Zardus with a serious expression on her face and in 
her voice.

"So what's the plan? Infiltrate and destroy?"
